name: weight
description_lines: Weight to assign to the specified service.
Minimum value = 1
Maximum value = 100

name: name
description_lines: Name for the virtual server. Must begin with an ASCII alphanumeric or underscore (_) character, and must contain only ASCII alphanumeric, underscore, hash (#), period (.), space, colon (:), at sign (@), equal sign (=), and hyphen (-) characters. Can be changed after the virtual server is created. CLI Users: If the name includes one or more spaces, enclose the name in double or single quotation marks (for example, "my vserver" or 'my vserver'). .
Minimum length = 1

name: servicename
description_lines: Service to bind to the virtual server.
Minimum length = 1

name: servicegroupname
description_lines: Name of the service group.
Minimum length = 1

name: preferredlocation
description_lines: Used for displaying the location of bound services.

name: vserverid
description_lines: Vserver Id.

name: vsvrbindsvcip
description_lines: used for showing the ip of bound entities.

name: servicetype
description_lines: Protocol used by the service (also called the service type).

Possible values = HTTP, FTP, TCP, UDP, SSL, SSL_BRIDGE, SSL_TCP, DTLS, NNTP, DNS, DHCPRA, ANY, SIP_UDP, SIP_TCP, SIP_SSL, DNS_TCP, RTSP, PUSH, SSL_PUSH, RADIUS, RDP, MYSQL, MSSQL, DIAMETER, SSL_DIAMETER, TFTP, ORACLE, SMPP, SYSLOGTCP, SYSLOGUDP, FIX, SSL_FIX

name: cookieipport
description_lines: Encryped Ip address and port of the service that is inserted into the set-cookie http header.

name: port
description_lines: Port number for the virtual server.
Range 1 - 65535
* in CLI is represented as 65535 in NITRO API

name: vsvrbindsvcport
description_lines: used for showing ports of bound entities.
Range 1 - 65535
* in CLI is represented as 65535 in NITRO API

choices: DOWN WHEN GOING OUT OF SERVICE
name: curstate
description_lines: Current LB vserver state.
Possible values = UP, DOWN, UNKNOWN, BUSY, OUT OF SERVICE, GOING OUT OF SERVICE, DOWN WHEN GOING OUT OF SERVICE, NS_EMPTY_STR, Unknown, DISABLED

name: ipv46
description_lines: IPv4 or IPv6 address to assign to the virtual server.

name: dynamicweight
description_lines: Dynamic weight.

name: __count
description_lines: count parameter
